      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my go-to for weekend cruises and has never let me down. She\u2019s got a few tiny 'character marks' from the road, but honestly, once you\u2019re behind the wheel and feel how smooth she handles, you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that\u2019s been cared for by someone who truly loves driving. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you in the driver\u2019s seat!",
      "price": 33800.0,
