    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a meticulously sorted enthusiast build centered around a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant. The powerband is exceptionally linear, benefiting from a recent top-end refresh and recalibrated variable valve timing to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been dialed in with high-durometer polyurethane bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to eliminate deflection during high-G cornering. Equipped with a short-throw shifter and a lightweight flywheel, the drivetrain offers immediate throttle response and surgical gear engagement. This isn't just a commuter; it\u2019s a mechanically robust machine with optimized suspension geometry designed for precision turn-in and total composure at the limit.",
